game.name: Ice Princess Halloween Preps
game.description:
Halloween is approaching you and your favorite princess Elsa looks very excited to celebrate it on her own style! Hey ladies! Her wardrobe is full of the spooky items and accessories to now since she has fed up with carrying a look of a glossy princess. This is the first time when she is trying to wear the spooky look so the princess needs your help. Would you help her out? Join Ice Princess Halloween Preps and be prepared to guide her to pick up the perfect scary dresses and makeup!

 The best part is that you will find a huge variety of spooky dresses and accessories in her wardrobe. Be careful since she is already getting very late for the Halloween party! Firstly, browse through her gorgeous costumes and help her find out the one that suits her personality the most. Give your girl an elegant little black outfit, unicorn-shaped costumes, or pumpkin-shaped dresses and combine them with the matching scary hats and other horror items in this html5 dressing game!

Your job does not end when you finalize her spooky look since you also have to help her select a nice Halloween themed makeup in this brand new Halloween girls game. Her final look will depend upon your intense fashion skills. So no need to shy and try to mix and match as many items as you can to make her look scary and celebrate the festival like never before. Try out more funny and tricky Halloween based games that are available online for free to play without download!
